title: Already Breaking - after 3 months
body: I bought a pair of these headphones around 4 years ago and they lasted for over 3 years, I thought they were great value and I was really impressed. So when they eventually broke I bought the same pair again, but my new headphones have already broken in around 3 months, the sound cuts off if the wire is not in the exact right position and there''s often a lot of static noises.Considering the price, I shouldn't be surprised but it is disappointing, I recommend going for a different pair
